{"id": "1514501960416366642", "channel_id": "1514501960416366642", "type": 0, "author_id": "256852230685196288", "author_name": "shrike784", "author_bot": false, "content": "Honestly, I've been wondering why they put this menu for long time because it's useless to me. and now... check it please.", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T05:30:05.449000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-11T05:31:01.698000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Sarah_shock", "emoji_id": "1356053088552747141", "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1514501960622014484", "filename": "20216E1.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 433980, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1514501960416366642/1514501960622014484/20216E1.JPG?ex=6a2c421d&is=6a2af09d&hm=78ac88f3028b79b6888af49d8a8c4663d7e44863463b3faffc84af814053f0b6&"}, {"id": "1514501961091907605", "filename": "2001011.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 462670, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1514501960416366642/1514501961091907605/2001011.JPG?ex=6a2c421d&is=6a2af09d&hm=0a72398ed6d3e4442b3df3a89333641d5a3f5fac26b2fab68a25eb237edd3f1c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514501960416366642", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "\"Team Information\" didn't display in Korean client", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1514490847847256114", "channel_id": "1514490847847256114", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164303137293729792", "author_name": "spooky_penguin_", "author_bot": false, "content": "Can I get some clarification on how this works\nDoes it only count on symbiosis removed from entering ultra turn?\nIs it additive with other base damage Clementine gets?\nDoes it stay for the whole exploration stage and not a single battle?", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T04:45:56.006000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Jenkin_think", "emoji_id": "1459079611131494543", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1514490848388186112", "filename": "Untitled80_20260605180715.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2954538, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1514490847847256114/1514490848388186112/Untitled80_20260605180715.png?ex=6a2c37c4&is=6a2ae644&hm=502dcfd740796fc4262a8902829f4ff14eae8113f33593c4097f20e342f3f264&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514490847847256114", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Clarification on Clementine's E2", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1514490905422467144", "channel_id": "1514490847847256114", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164303137293729792", "author_name": "spooky_penguin_", "author_bot": false, "content": "Does her symbiosis removal scaling stay per battle? Or is it just a one time base dmg increase per exalt if you remove 20 stacks?", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T04:46:09.733000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514490847847256114", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Clarification on Clementine's E2", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1514572649219489853", "channel_id": "1514490847847256114", "type": 0, "author_id": "231543819026300928", "author_name": "crowlov1", "author_bot": false, "content": "Id test it. But I don't want to get E2 Clem.\n\nThe way it's worded. The first should stay only for the battle. So like infinite scaling like usual.\n\nBest thing you can do is load into arc1 content with no wheels and covs and even making sure you don't trigger her STR gain effects.\n\nGet 1 or however many symbiote stacks. And then either let them time out on their own or use exalt to remove them. (For this sake let's do 10 stacks)\n\nIf in both cases you end up with the same number. That will mean it counts stacks that you let time out.\n\nAfterwards. When you enter the second battle your exalt should be ever so slightly less DMG since that modifier is +25%. In comparison to the +30% you got from your removal of the stacks in that battle. If the number for whatever reason you have much bigger starting exalt DMG then you found a bug.", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T10:10:58.973000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-11T10:14:52.438000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514490847847256114", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Clarification on Clementine's E2", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1514572916048789515", "channel_id": "1514490847847256114", "type": 0, "author_id": "231543819026300928", "author_name": "crowlov1", "author_bot": false, "content": "Best to calculate the scaling before hand and if the calculation you made is correct, you should enter the battle and see that number.", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T10:12:02.590000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1514490847847256114", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Clarification on Clementine's E2", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
